body:
It seems I used [SingleThreadedCpuDevice](../tree/master/tensorflow/core/common_runtime/single_threaded_cpu_device.h) that was added in 9b18bd70b5739d646b21b7d45de0e5c96b8cc2a1, later than when [ScopedAllocator](../tree/master/tensorflow/core/common_runtime/scoped_allocator.cc) was added in 282750fee5e2df502436ca9ef6a95283f8adab34.

@skye Mind to fix this? Or I could help submit a patch if you're okay with it.

EDIT: turns out it's the problem of [RenamedDevice](../tree/master/tensorflow/core/common_runtime/renamed_device.h).
